title: Tribe launches new Cherokee Language Dictionary app with advanced learning tools
description: TAHLEQUAH — Cherokee Nation leaders and Cherokee language speakers joined representatives of Kiwa Digital Ltd. to unveil the new Cherokee Language Dictionary app during a celebration at Durbin Feeling Language Center in Tahlequah, Tuesday, Dec. 9.
